@baseUrl = http://localhost:8081

### API - listar tasks (atalho)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api
Accept: application/json

### API - listar tasks
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks
Accept: application/json

### API - buscar task por id (valido)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/1
Accept: application/json

### API - buscar task inexistente
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/99999
Accept: application/json

### API - metodo nao permitido (deve retornar 404 no router atual)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Nova task de teste"
}
